{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-list-tsx","path":"/tags/FastAPI/","result":{"data":{"allMdx":{"nodes":[{"excerpt":"笔者性格使然，并不太介意个人隐私，愿意把自己的各种进行时的状态信息公开展示在个人网站上。很早以前，笔者就想要实现一个小软件，它能自动读取在电脑上运转的程序，将当前活跃的程序名称上传到网站上进行展示。但是遗憾没有好的实现思路，最终只是新建了 Repo 就搁置了这个想法。 如今，随着全局代理成为家中网络标配，Discord 成为挂驻后台的常用软件，看着自己信息页的“正在玩”项目…","fields":{"slug":"display-my-discord-status"},"frontmatter":{"banner":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#5878e8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/a764f/banner.jpg","srcSet":"/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/fb67e/banner.jpg 480w,\n/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/3059d/banner.jpg 960w,\n/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/a764f/banner.jpg 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/3a3a2/banner.webp 480w,\n/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/bde8a/banner.webp 960w,\n/static/b143f4885662830e0bdb23349cc93e8a/c512e/banner.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":1080}}},"categories":["软件开发"],"tags":["Discord","Bot","Python","FastAPI"],"title":"实时读取自己的 Discord 状态，供前端应用展示","date":"2025-11-14T00:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-11-20T00:00:00.000Z","timeliness":null}}]}},"pageContext":{"ids":["133cf655-7ffc-5eae-b086-3fd1494bce87"],"tag":"FastAPI"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2291570122","267559364"],"slicesMap":{}}